video_prompt: An anime rock star sways, strumming an electric guitar. Her platinum hair flows as she moves, eyes subtly shifting. Her lips part slightly, a teardrop earring glints. Hands articulate across the guitar, chain swaying from her belt. The background subtly undulates with cloudy, starlit movements.
